                                                     file structure
     
     
     
             UNISWP byte definitions
     
                     |---------------------------------------|
                     | Addr next UDB    |  |CFS|    K4S      |
                     |  for swapping    |  |   |             |
                     |---------------------------------------|
                      0               17    20  23         35
     
                     Word            Byte
                     Label   Bits    Pointer         Content
                     ------  -----   -------         -------
                     UNISWP  0-17                    Address of the next unit data
                                                     block to be used for swapping
                     UNICFS  20-22   UNYCFS          Swapping class
